    introduction: "I pray for you that you receive help as you trust God for your provisions in spiritual and material things in the name of Jesus Christ, Amen. When you seek help from God, you will always enjoy help from above and abroad. When you seek help from Satan, he will supply it to your detriment and ruin. It is only help from God that comes exceeding abundantly above all that you ask or think. Meaning, His help lifts you above lack, misery and penury. His help empowers you to stay on top and prosperous in faith and life. God does this so that His glory will be in the church and spread out throughout the ages/world without end, Amen. Seek His help in times of trials and challenges and God will prove to you that He is able to go beyond your wildest imagination to bring help or solution above your situation. Amen.",
    prayer_focus: "Heavenly father, from now I know, as I turn to you in time of stress or loss, you will upkeep me with enough and to spare.",
