      "I pray for you that you will be one of the vessels God will use to win souls into His kingdom in this remaining part of this year and onward in Jesus name, Amen. Soul Winning is the greatest job on earth. One thing is certain; he/she who must win souls must first allow his/her own soul to be won to Christ. There is no gain in one winning souls but loosing his/her own soul. Soul winning is a job to be taken seriously by the Church via the Evangelism ministry.",
